  "description": "SCAP/OVAL mappings to NIST SP 800-53 Rev 5. Three resolution tiers: (1) OVAL test types for precise matching, (2) OVAL families for broad classification, (3) XCCDF keyword categories as fallback. Derived from ComplianceAsCode rule patterns and OVAL schema definitions.",
